\f1\b0 : This creates a guided visual flow that draws attention down the page naturally. Since your platform is about discovery, this helps users "discover" each section as they scroll.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs19\fsmilli9756 \cf0 2. Directory Card Hover Effects\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa180\partightenfactor0

\fs21 \cf0 What
\f1\b0 : Subtle scale and shadow changes when users hover over directory cards, perhaps with a gentle color shift using your theme variables.\

\f0\b How
\f1\b0 : Using Tailwind's group-hover classes combined with your theme variables to create transitions that are consistent with each directory's brand colors.\

\f0\b Why it fits
\f1\b0 : This provides immediate visual feedback that enhances discoverability while maintaining the professional feel appropriate for emergency services directories.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs19\fsmilli9756 \cf0 3. Animated Divider Expansion\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa180\partightenfactor0

\fs21 \cf0 What
