\f0\b Why it fits
\f1\b0 : This draws attention to the separation between your hero messaging and the practical directory options, emphasizing the transition from "why" to "what".\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs19\fsmilli9756 \cf0 4. Subtle Background Gradient Shifts\
